metadata.name: Data
metadata.description:
Data

Represents {Table} Data as a list of name/value pairs. Also contains metadata such as etag and total.

metadata.name: kind
metadata.description: The resource type of the API response.

metadata.name: etag
metadata.description: A hash of this page of results.

metadata.name: total
metadata.description: The total number of rows in the complete table.

metadata.name: next?
metadata.description: Is there a next page of data?

metadata.name: raw
metadata.description: Represents Table Data as a list of positional values (array of arrays). No type conversion is made, e.g. numbers are formatted as strings.

metadata.name: format_rows
metadata.description: rubocop:disable all Disabled rubocop because this implementation will not last.

metadata.name: ensure_table!
metadata.description: Raise an error unless an active connection is available.
